   <title>迁移到版本8.4.11</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 8.4.X.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   运行8.4.X不需要备份/恢复。
