   为Bangladesh, Egypt, Mauritius中DST变化规律更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>发布2009l。
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-4">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Release 8.4</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>版本8.4</title>

  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <para>2009-07-01</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <para>2009-07-01</para>
  </formalpara>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Overview</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>概要</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    After many years of development, <productname>PostgreSQL</> has
    become feature-complete in many areas.   This release shows a
    targeted approach to adding features (e.g., authentication,
    monitoring, space reuse), and adds capabilities defined in the
    later SQL standards.  The major areas of enhancement are:
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    经过多年研发后，<productname>PostgreSQL</>已经在许多领域特性比较完整。
该发布显示一个针对性方法来添加特性（比如，认证，监测，空间重利用），
并且添加在以后SQL标准中定义的能力。增强的主要方面是：
</para>

   <itemizedlist>

    <!-- This list duplicates items below, but without authors or details-->

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Windowing Functions
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    窗口函数
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Common Table Expressions and Recursive Queries
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   通用表表达式和递归查询
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Default and variadic parameters for functions
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    函数缺省和可变参数
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Parallel Restore
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    并行恢复
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Column Permissions
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    列权限
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Per-database locale settings
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   每个数据库本地设置
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improved hash indexes
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    改进的哈希索引
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improved join performance for <literal>EXISTS</> and <literal>NOT EXISTS</> queries
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    改进<literal>EXISTS</>和<literal>NOT EXISTS</>查询连接性能
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Easier-to-use Warm Standby
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    容易使用热备份
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Automatic sizing of the Free Space Map
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    空闲空间映射的自动大小
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Visibility Map (greatly reduces vacuum overhead for slowly-changing tables)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   可见映射（大大降低了缓慢变化表的清理开销）
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Version-aware psql (backslash commands work against older servers)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    版本感知psql(旧服务器之前使用反斜杠命令)
</para>
    </listitem>

